<section style="margin: -11px 0px; padding: 20px 15px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 253, 246);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(239, 75, 75); background: transparent;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(172, 29, 16); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">为了学习贯彻习近平总书记在党的二十届二中全会上的重要讲话和全会精神，进一步引导党员同志学深悟透精神内涵，把握实践要求。2023年4月11日晚7时，我院学生党支部于经济管理学院党员活动室组织学生党支部例会，会议由学生党支部组织委员黄山松同志主持，学生党员参与。</span></p></section></section></section><p></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;"><section data-width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 574px; border-top: 2px solid rgb(239, 75, 75); height: 2px; overflow: hidden;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 248, 215); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section><p></p><p><span style="color: rgb(33, 33, 34); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 243, 221); font-size: 24px;">本次支部会议中黄山松同志带领大家集中学习，在持续全面学习贯彻落实的基础上，深入学习宣传贯彻党的二十届二中全会精神。会议强调，作为学生党员应把学习贯彻党的二十届二中全会和全国两会精神作为当前和今后一个时期的重要任务，认真学习、深入领会、准确把握全会精神，更加坚定拥护“两个确立”、坚决做到“两个维护”，迅速把全会精神传内化于心、外化于行，推动学习宣传贯彻不断往深里走、往实里走。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(33, 33, 34); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(255, 243, 221); font-size: 24px;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEJZLUmm7bAFkzzPCecRjkUibSrRaQK2WlMPGicZATiazwtJb9UCq3yibmjThVWqyTHaK5PkrO7ia7MfM4g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="485" height="261" style="width: 485px; height: 261px;"/></span></p>